56
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:21,964
Uh, no, no. Wait,
wait, hold on a minute.

57
00:02:21,966 --> 00:02:24,333
<i>I'm hungry, I'll meet you at Pop's.</i>

58
00:02:24,335 --> 00:02:25,434
