235
00:11:29,090 --> 00:11:33,292
And I wouldn't be surprised
if it was the same man.

236
00:11:33,694 --> 00:11:34,994
[TEARS PAPER]

237
00:11:35,529 --> 00:11:36,762
Here's the check,

238
00:11:36,764 --> 00:11:37,830
